mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">{!Account.Name}</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;
