mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">{!Account.BillingCity},&nbsp;{!Account.BillingCountry}</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;
mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">Madame, Monsieur&nbsp;<span style="background:white">{!Account.Name}</span>,</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:13.8pt"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">Le
26<span style="background:white">&nbsp;mars 2018</span>,&nbsp;la résolution 812
ayant trait à la nouvelle génération des systèmes de règlement de l’IATA
(NewGen ISS) entrera en vigueur <span style="background:white">{!Account.BillingCountry}.&nbsp;</span>Cette
nouvelle résolution concerne les règles des agences de vente en vertu des
NewGen ISS et introduit un nouveau programme qui modernisera le BSP de manière
à mieux répondre aux besoins de l’industrie du voyage en offrant plus de choix
et de latitude à leurs agents<a name="_ftnref1"></a><a href="file:///C:/Users/hazbounc/Desktop/Final%20TIDS%20pacakage/14%20Feb%202018/Level2_Segregation%20of%20TIDS%20BR%20V2_20180208.docx#_ftn1" title=""><span style="color:blue">[1]</span></a>.</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:13.8pt"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">&nbsp;</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;
mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">De manière à ce que la communauté des agences de
voyages profite et valorise pleinement les avantages des NewGen ISS, on a
déterminé qu’il fallait harmoniser les dispositions de la </span><span lang="FR"><a href="http://www.iata.org/Sites/FMC/Files/reso_898.pdf"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: windowtext; text-decoration-line: none;">Résolution 898</span></a></span><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">
et séparer complètement le Service d'identification de l'industrie touristique
(TIDS) des sièges sociaux des agences de voyages.</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;
mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">Selon nos dossiers, votre agence s’est vue attribuer
des codes TIDS en tant que divisions de votre siège social détenant un code
IATA <span style="background:white">{!Account.IATACode__c}.</span>&nbsp;</span><span lang="FR"><a href="file:///C:/Users/hazbounc/Desktop/Final%20TIDS%20pacakage/14%20Feb%202018/Level2_Segregation%20of%20TIDS%20BR%20V2_20180208.docx#_ftn2"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: windowtext; text-decoration-line: none;">[2]</span></a></span><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">.
</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;background:white;
mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">Ainsi donc, afin de
s’harmoniser en vertu des dispositions de la </span><span lang="FR"><a href="http://www.iata.org/Sites/FMC/Files/reso_898.pdf"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: windowtext; background: white; text-decoration-line: none;">Résolution
898</span></a></span><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;background:white;
mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">, en vigueur à compter du 21
mars</span><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;
mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">, vos codes TIDS seront graduellement séparés du code
de l’agence IATA et convertis selon l’une des options suivantes&nbsp;: </span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><ul type="disc">
 <li class="MsoNormal"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:
     FR-CA">Option 1 – Un siège social TIDS indépendant</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class="MsoNormal"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:
     FR-CA">Option 2 – Une hiérarchie TIDS comportant un siège social TIDS et
     les autres TIDS restant en tant que divisions associées de ce siège
     social.</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;
     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:13.8pt"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">Afin
de faciliter ce processus de conformité, veuillez nous fournir l’information
suivante avant le <b>20 mars 2018</b>&nbsp;:</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:13.8pt"><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.5in;line-height:13.8pt"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;I.
Votre option privilégiée comme indiqué ci-dessus (Option 1 ou 2)</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.5in;line-height:13.8pt"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;II.&nbsp;Le
code TIDS que vous désirez choisir en tant que siège social TIDS (dans le cas
de l’option 2)</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;
margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.5in;line-height:13.8pt"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;III.&nbsp;La
personne-ressource parmi votre liste de contacts existants à être affectée au
siège social TIDS, car il est possible que nous ayons besoin de communiquer
directement avec votre siège social TIDS indépendant.&nbsp; Par ailleurs, vous pouvez fournir une
nouvelle personne-ressource ayant une adresse de courriel unique.</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:13.8pt"><u><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">Si
l’information requise ci-dessus n’est pas reçue d’ici le 20 mars 2018, vos
codes TIDS seront convertis en une hiérarchie TIDS où le siège social sera
choisi au hasard par IATA à partir de vos codes TIDS actifs actuels. </span></u><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:13.8pt"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">&nbsp;</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:13.8pt"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">Une
fois les NewGen ISS opérationnels, l’IATA offrira aux agents le choix des types
d’accréditation suivants&nbsp;: </span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><ul type="disc">
 <li class="MsoNormal"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:
     FR-CA">Accréditation Golite (une accréditation standard sans facilité de
     financement)</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;
     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class="MsoNormal"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:
     FR-CA">Accréditation GoStandard (accréditation standard avec facilité de
     financement)</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;
     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:13.8pt"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">Vos
sites TIDS sont libres de demander une de ces accréditations une fois que les
NewGen ISS seront opérationnels dans vos marchés BSP respectifs, ou de
continuer d’être des sites TIDS indépendants.</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:13.8pt"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">L’accréditation
de vos sites TIDS, quels que soient les types d’accréditation, devra respecter
les critères d’accréditation IATA applicables et à l’annulation des codes TIDS
alors que des codes IATA leur seront assignés.</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:13.8pt"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">Si
vous soumettez une demande en deçà de 90 jours de la date de transmission en
direct des NewGen ISS, l’accréditation de n’importe lequel de vos sites TIDS
n’entraînera pas de frais supplémentaires. Pour amorcer le processus, vous
pouvez contacter l’IATA au moyen du portail de service à la clientèle en direct
à </span><span lang="FR"><a href="file:///C:/Users/palaobasb/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Temporary%20Internet%20Files/Content.Outlook/PPIHN801/www.iata.org/cs"><b><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: windowtext; text-decoration-line: none;">www.iata.org/cs</span></b></a></span><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">.</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:13.8pt"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">Si
vous avez d’autres questions, veuillez les formuler au moyen du Portail de
service à la clientèle d’IATA (</span><span lang="FR"><a href="http://www.iata.org/cs"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
color:windowtext;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">www.iata.org/cs</span></a></span><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">).
Notre équipe du Service client vous assistera avec plaisir.</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
