color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-bidi-language:FR-CA">Centre global
d’expédition IATA</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span><span lang="FR" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="FR-CA" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>
